                    <p> While you wait to receive news of your pet from us, here are some recommendations given by The Humane Society of THE UNITED STATES in their article, "What to do if you lose your pet". </p>
                    <p> #1 - Contact local shelters and animal control agencies</p>
                    <p> #2 - Search the neighborhood</p>
                    <p> #3 - Advertise</p>
                    <p> #4 - Be wary of pet-recovery scams</p>
                    <p> #5 - Don't give up your search</p>
                    <a href="https://www.humanesociety.org/resources/what-do-if-you-lose-your-pet#:~:text=File%20a%20lost%20pet%20report,contact%20the%20local%20police%20department."> To read the full article from The Humane Society of THE UNITED STATES, click here </a>
